---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="eyebrow">Drummer — Zurich</p>
      <h1>David <span class="ink">Krähenbühl</span></h1>
      <p class="bio">
        <!-- TODO Dave: replace with your own bio text (2-4 sentences). -->
        David Krähenbühl is a drummer from Zurich, working as an in-demand
        sideman and as co-bandleader of the instrumental trio loophole. His
        playing is groovy and atmospheric, shaped by musicians such as
        BADBADNOTGOOD, Yussef Dayes, and Tom Misch.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-media">
      <!-- TODO Dave: replace /public/images/hero.jpg -->
      <img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="David Krähenbühl playing drums" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: clamp(3rem, 9vw, 7rem);
  }
  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    align-items: end;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  h1 .ink {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .bio {
    max-width: var(--measure);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .hero-media img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    object-fit: cover;
    background: var(--surface);
  }
  @media (max-width: 780px) {
    .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; align-items: start; }
    .hero-media { order: -1; max-width: 68%; }
  }
</style>
